  <summary>2/6/1997--Introduced.
White House Fund-Raising Prohibition Act of 1997 - Prohibits any person from soliciting, receiving, or rewarding a political contribution on the grounds or in the buildings, including private residential areas, of an official residence or retreat of the President or Vice-President.</summary>
